title: [dnceng-bot] Branch `msbuild/exp/9303-use-load-with-fallback2` can't be mirrored to Azdo fast forward branch
body:
Branch [exp/9303-use-load-with-fallback2](https://github.com/DotNet/msbuild/commits/exp/9303-use-load-with-fallback2/) in `DotNet/msbuild` repo can't be mirrored from GitHub to Azure DevOps [exp/9303-use-load-with-fallback2](https://dev.azure.com/devdiv/DevDiv/_git/DotNet-msbuild-Trusted?version=GBexp%2F9303-use-load-with-fallback2&_a=history) via fast forward. 
There was unexpected error during the mirroring process.
            
failed to connect to dev.azure.com: Network is unreachable

Problem need to be **resolved to unblock the code flow**.

You can troubleshoot the issue by:
- checking the logs of the mirroring process in the [mirroring pipeline](https://dev.azure.com/dnceng/internal/_build?definitionId=1391).
- by trying to mirror the branch manually
- you can disable the mirroring of the branch in the [configuration file](https://dev.azure.com/dnceng/internal/_git/dotnet-mirroring?path=/devdiv-subscriptions.jsonc).
- you can ask @dotnet/dnceng for help or read the [documentation](https://dev.azure.com/dnceng/internal/_git/dotnet-mirroring?path=/README.md).

Please close this issue once the problem is resolved.

nodes.body: @ladipro do you still need this exp branch?
If not, I suggest deleting it and closing the issue
I have deleted exp/9303-use-load-with-fallback2 and a few more unused experimental branches. Closing.
